title: Europa Universalis.IV.Art.Of.War
description:
Europa Universalis IV: Art Of War

This release uses a modified codex.ini file from the previously released: Europa.Universalis.IV.Res.Publica-CODEX

Please note, THIS IS NOT AN OFFICIAL CODEX RELEASE, if you want that version, wait for it.

This version includes all the previous DLCS from the Res.Publica CODEX release as well as the recently released Art Of War expansion and patch 1.8

If you don't trust, don't download, I'm not even going to bother explaining
